  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">\"C'mon, let's crack some skulls!\"</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">Wuthering Waves &times; Cyberpunk: Edgerunners Collaboration is set to launch on June 8th (UTC+8).</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"3\" data-line=\"true\">The new 5-Star Resonators Lucy and Rebecca will debut, and you can snag the 5-Star Resonator Rebecca for free!</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1779984000000/0mxk2ss0d8vklz7zvp-1780067540593.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1779984000000/v48i1glrzzuhggabye-1780067558057.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1779984000000/vi64nnmrjkh6qgcs7b-1780067649464.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></strong></span><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1779984000000/yfpn98en6uu1c5dp1o-1780067913095.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc